{"id": "d5d891a64f5fafcd1909abe81641931d43eb0866332e0859903b906ee8bbc979", "item_id": "500a074c24:0", "text": "For Rendering to Disk only. Checkpoints and recovery are ignored for interactive rendering."}
{"id": "48f6a8d5688b0cf59fb8109b7903507ed9d2e1580be2ad7ae169df659e1ddeea", "item_id": "500a074c24:1", "text": "Recovery"}
{"id": "bf9d2556b11fce31bd9cfaf6f9026f227016bd735c8ca8e659efcbfe1f6c59b5", "item_id": "500a074c24:2", "text": "Recovery allows us to resume/recover from the previously paused or incomplete stopped render.  To turn it on, check"}
{"id": "bfb1c0c2afed827b250fcdb9c2b7412721a8152b96c695529ffd1f14f2a2b6c1", "item_id": "500a074c24:9", "text": "Recover Render"}
{"id": "69bed302490ee5f6fe2341489c4a6deffe0d01dcba2a8fd543d36ac9e2b2c004", "item_id": "500a074c24:10", "text": "in RenderMan RIS ROP's"}
{"id": "8aa915a9c5d88236afd43ad6005c1f50b4b9ef4801926d188df926c52ea2dc61", "item_id": "500a074c24:6", "text": "Tab."}
{"id": "d76c241e62e34c37286cca0ea89df6e300f324bf357aebc622c5d55a3e375af9", "item_id": "500a074c24:7", "text": "Checkpoints"}
{"id": "eeecea2631d0009506b3593c1e823f38b28cf0583f6cf62f05b187d4a9640aa3", "item_id": "500a074c24:8", "text": "Render recovery is often used with checkpointing.  To turn it on, check"}
{"id": "6d89eb7d0938564938636b4a5ee73c09e55c2e6e5aaa9e3016781bf54805e8d3", "item_id": "500a074c24:12", "text": "Render"}
{"id": "90ddf1963abb36c9921ce7f1ac9cbd94c9176d13e57c418d3d3c20ce44291c1c", "item_id": "500a074c24:13", "text": "Tab"}
{"id": "745a4d143466fa7af8bef286eabec1ce58cab0ebbb28f34d49b7f2f6f036dd26", "item_id": "500a074c24:15", "text": "Interval - the time between checkpoint saves"}
{"id": "ad31e6f3746778af66ecc97e81fef9c72907537adae4abcc5767aac8a564a5ee", "item_id": "500a074c24:16", "text": "Exit At - Exit the render at this time and render no more"}
{"id": "184e2214ecfc7b8125411fa3f8edbcc9a4320bba245670a9c94bed8c60b7fb7f", "item_id": "500a074c24:17", "text": "As Final - Even if the render completes, save the data necessary to pick up the render. This will result in a larger file"}
{"id": "c71c7c0a44ec62440322c07a240b838fb7a7b2ff5c5c0d882213e37c1ca35de8", "item_id": "500a074c24:18", "text": "Keep Files - Name and preserve all the past checkpoints instead of only the more recent one"}
{"id": "e259689327d6cbed1614ef9578494ca5f7e7e6579819c66d0087674cf7e8b69c", "item_id": "500a074c24:19", "text": "Command - Command for the RIB file location (if one is generated)"}
{"id": "3db70c9eda79f755b9fa1aaf0d67a9a6d9bbe72deaf8b6bc1c471037658bca7d", "item_id": "500a074c24:20", "text": "Incremental Renders"}
{"id": "e42917fbbb19c5224740c5bcc89b94567b0b294bf36b4ebe55d261c9d9c9671f", "item_id": "500a074c24:21", "text": "Incremental renders are not recoverable without checkpointing enabled. With incremental on and checkpoints off, the buckets are not written out until the end of the render. See table below:"}
{"id": "80a3df68e540126042ce0a4f70667d78a556fd6f19398efbbebb31aef87cd449", "item_id": "500a074c24:22", "text": "incremental"}
{"id": "6c7f546429ec5c55a4c3162aa9ce0b262b6985b998c23f781ffbc1b890851794", "item_id": "500a074c24:23", "text": "checkpoints"}
{"id": "4e9e8bb939136f139c0830a0c33ef4faddc541261dba7a58effb41a4302f88dd", "item_id": "500a074c24:24", "text": "recoverable"}
{"id": "130011756125313c72f2cab730db4347e2841526d236a89cb25f38789fa49229", "item_id": "500a074c24:28", "text": "On"}
{"id": "75081b593d15cf6e631971bc6768723f593b88b172477e40ae7d363e4829816d", "item_id": "500a074c24:32", "text": "Disabled"}
{"id": "1ea442a134b2a184bd5d40104401f2a37fbc09ccf3f4bc9da161c6099be3691d", "item_id": "500a074c24:27", "text": "No"}
{"id": "85a39ab345d672ff8ca9b9c6876f3adcacf45ee7c1e2dbd2408fd338bd55e07e", "item_id": "500a074c24:36", "text": "Yes"}
{"id": "ca7981b46ecf2c1787b6d76d81d9fd7fa0ca95842e2fcc2a452869891a9334d1", "item_id": "500a074c24:34", "text": "Off"}
{"id": "205bfdc723f3fdb5287ab18261c6c1aae401ccca307f504de3d475a6c7addb8c", "item_id": "500a074c24:37", "text": "Recoverable Render Settings"}
{"id": "9c72ed0556fff5b3084c723fc17370bcff16f3057aedd675086f767f904750b7", "item_id": "500a074c24:38", "text": "Recovery and 'keepfiles'"}
{"id": "72061d743bf251ea6cf24a01d0f2155d11af28d6807430a66b89ad5ecec87373", "item_id": "500a074c24:39", "text": "Do not enable the keepfiles option for checkpointing if you want to use the recover capability."}
{"id": "f08ade8e7848dd0ff4f1fd69d794c70da957cb8b1a8a0d97e84dc3825341f879", "item_id": "500a074c24:40", "text": "Option \"checkpoint\" \"uniform int keepfiles\" [0]"}
{"id": "012a51ef88f50b048afeede728f0224ef2613dd838ea74f7413502ecf5300ded", "item_id": "500a074c24:41", "text": "The keepfiles option causes prman to save a sequence of checkpoints for debugging purposes giving each checkpoint image a unique file name tagged with increment and elapsed render time. However, when attempting to recover a file, prman won't scan your directory for checkpointed files or try to choose one. It will only look for the file by the original render output name."}
